.IP \(bu 2
\fB\fCtime1_format\fR, \fB\fCtime2_format\fR and \fB\fCclock_tooltip\fR use the 'strftime' syntax. More info can be found here: \[la]http://www.manpagez.com/man/3/strftime/\[ra]
